          "description": "Excellent. Absolutely excellent. The Doctors and the Staff are incredible. They should walk and all of us clap as we did for Covid. Dr Henry Ackerman went out of his way to be nice, gentle, explain in simple words everything. Dr Alex Bonilla, the same. He also would come and tell me what would happen next and why. Before that, every nurse and staff member was kind, had a smile when talking to patients. Doctors go to school for so many years and the main satisfaction they have is not money, is to cure. I saw it first hand.  I travel a lot and try to document hospitals. Curious what\u2019s inside like? Take a look. I made sure not to show any faces, just the facilities. I am a Global CFO and teach at NYU. I go around the world telling HS kids \u201cgo to college\u201d. A few weeks ago, one HS asked me \u201cI want to be a doctor. Is it a good idea?\u201d From now on, I\u2019ll be able to tell them why is a yes. Thanks to everyone at this hospital. It\u2019s excellent",
