          "description": "Came in around 11am. Wasn't too busy yet. Had sharp pain in lower abdomen. Was able to get urine analysis, blood work, and a CT scan with contrast all in about two hours. Nurse staff and doctors were professional, kind, and helpful. Out the door in under three hours and paid on the spot. Wonderful service.",
