          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPR9xDZ2tc-etrFQ0JRPYECDH1sgvuNpHIyhUdJ9JLklwxuMVtqw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "Do not go here unless you won\u2019t survive by trying to go anywhere else. They are so disorganized. I was brought to a room and left there with no call button or anything for 90 minutes before a nurse came to check on me. They admitted they forgot to assign a nurse to me. Barely had any face time with any doctors. But when I did, there were 2 different doctors who weren\u2019t communicating with each other and providing different treatment plans. I left feeling worse and more confused. This wasn\u2019t a one off. I was here last year for a different emergency and it was the same shit. Truly don\u2019t come here unless you\u2019re bleeding out and won\u2019t survive trying to make it anywhere else. And if then, they\u2019ll probably not see you or do anything for you for 2 hours.",
