          "description": "The doctors were so kind. Dr. Jennifer beck, Dr. Rajas karajgikar and Dr.paul grosrenaud helped me relocate my shoulder after a bad fall! They were attentive talked me through the entire process, carful with me and careful with my mental state! the x ray people were a bit tired. The emts were great! Emts in the ambulance let me know every bump and made sure I was okay! Stayed with me till nurses who were  stressed but understanding enough got me. I would recommend this emergency room if they aren\u2019t busy. They gave me good follow up too (lost my earring but through no fault of the staff)",
